data.description:
THIS HOME HAS IT ALL- MOVE-IN Ready

Nestled in desired Clay County, this beautiful move-in ready home boasts 3 bedrooms and  1 1/2 bathrooms. It features a spacious living/dining room combo, large kitchen with butcher block countertops, and wood cabinets.  It is ideally positioned on an oversized lot; and features a fully fenced backyard, with 120 sq ft. wood shed. The heated & cooled Florida room is the perfect spot for entertaining and an oversized laundry room make this home one-of-a- kind. HVAC installed in 2020, new water heater installed in 2023 and new windows installed in April 2023 throughout the house with lifetime warranty, and 17 inches of insulation blowing in 2022. For your security, home features an ADT security system. New shingles roof installed December 2023. 

Just Miles away from NAS JAX! VETERANS WELCOME
